dataList.content: Pallid bipedals began to fill the void Rim left behind.
It can be deduced that it was his influence that kept the Mermaids at bay.
I can only theorize that their primal sense of certain ebbs and flows of energy remained even as their reason eroded.
You're saying that he scared 'em off or something...?
The one who bisected Kromer with a flick of his wrist. The one who silently approached me to talk.
I remember the one marked with the bright red sign.
